<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./stely.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./bott.js" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.4/css/boxicons.min.css" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        .categories-bar {
            background: #f3a7b3;
            padding: 10px 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .category {
            background: white;
            color: #383838;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

            .category.active {
                background: #f09ab0;
                color: white;
            }

        .post-container {
            background-color: #f9cfdf !important;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

            .post-container img {
                width: 50%;
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

            .post-container .content {
                width: 50%;
                padding: 0 20px;
            }

            .post-container h2 {
                color: #b35a74;
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                margin-top: 10px;
            }

            .post-container p {
                color: #555;
            }

        .read-more {
            background-color: #F5A3B7;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

            .read-more:hover {
                background-color: #F5A3B7;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="categories-bar">
        <button class="category active">All Category</button>
        <button class="category">Ecofriendly</button>
        <button class="category">Organic</button>
        <button class="category">Tips</button>
        <button class="category">Compilation</button>
        <button class="category">Ingredients</button>
        <button class="category">Antiaging</button>
        <button class="category">Combination</button>
    </div>

    <main class="container mt-4">
        <div class="post-container">
			<img src="~/Images/pexels-photo-9748713.webp" />
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Cracking the Coconut Code</h2>
                <p>Few ingredients have been debated as much in recent years as coconut oil. Is it a trick or a treasure?</p>
                <button class="read-more">Read More</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="post-container flex-row-reverse">
			<img src="~/images/pexels-photo-6724448.jpeg" />
            <div class="content">
                <h2>Bloom Beauty Best of 2023</h2>
                <p>Can you believe we're here? Another year is wrapping up and we're feeling celebratory...</p>
                <button class="read-more">Read More</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="post-container">
