            <div class="content">
                <h2>Cracking the Coconut Code</h2>
                <p>Few ingredients have been debated as much in recent years as coconut oil. Is it a trick or a treasure?</p>
                <button class="read-more">Read More</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="post-container flex-row-reverse">
			<img src="~/images/vya-naturals-m3l24oeny2c-unsplash.jpg" />
