                <h2>Bloom Beauty Best of 2023</h2>
                <p>Can you believe we're here? Another year is wrapping up and we're feeling celebratory...</p>
                <button class="read-more">Read More</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
